about how I never get solos.

750
00:33:49,872 --> 00:33:51,005
(laughs)

751
00:33:51,039 --> 00:33:53,040
(crying)

752
00:33:57,713 --> 00:33:59,714
(laughing)

753
00:34:03,337 --> 00:34:04,904
Oh, I love you, Tina.

754
00:34:04,938 --> 00:34:06,506
(laughs)

755
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:07,774
Oh.

756
00:34:07,808 --> 00:34:09,509
(soft laugh)

757
00:34:09,543 --> 00:34:12,044
Now you listen to me.

758
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:15,248
You were there
in the choir room with us.

759
00:34:15,282 --> 00:34:16,816
Mm-hmm.
Okay?

