makes me drier

768
00:34:38,172 --> 00:34:39,806
than the cast
of <i>Hot in Cleveland.</i>

769
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:42,308
It's totally her.
Think of it.

770
00:34:42,342 --> 00:34:45,077
